O 9001:2015 certification for their management system.<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ-LLC became a member at Dubai Gold Jewelry Group.<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ-LLC with Dubai Police and Dubai Tourism with incorporation of DGJG installed QR Code Scan at Gateways to Dubai Gold Souq to simplify and support contact \u2013 less navigation where it will help our Gold Souq from spread of Covid-19.<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ \u2013 LLC \u201cMain Branch\u201d Manager received appreciation certificate for his contribution to the work done over the years with Dubai customs.<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ-LLC \u201cMain Branch\u201d awarded \u201cMestanes\u201d reward from Dubai Customs.<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ-LLC \u201cMain Branch\u201d Started production in their expanded production space at Dubai Production City and the total area became 22,000 Square feet (B-36 &amp; B-37).<\/li><li>Sam Precious Metals FZ-LLC \u201cMain Branch\u201d received <strong>ISO\/IEC 17025:2017 <\/strong>certification for their lab for sampling &amp; testing gold and silver using cupellation method, ICP &amp; XRF for gold. Cupellation method ICP, XRF and titration method for silver. <strong>ISO\/IEC 17025:2017<\/strong>\u00a0is regarded as one of the highest accreditations for professional precious metals laboratories.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9d88a7a elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"9d88a7a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3647442 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3647442\" data-element_type=\"